 I wonder if anybody's just arrived in Hong Kong.

7
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,000
 Maybe you're new to the city.

8
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:21,000
 Maybe you've come in in the last week or two or month,

9
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:23,000
 and you're settling into Hong Kong.

10
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,000
 It's totally new for you.

11
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,000
 Maybe you have your family.

12
