00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:07,000
 And you'll see that rhythm throughout all seven days of creation,

334
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:10,000
 but it's right there at the moment when God creates humanity.

335
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:15,000
 He speaks, he creates, he blesses, and he pronounces good.

336
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:17,000
 Now, here's what happens next.

337
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:20,000
 God has created humanity, and he says these words.

