00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:23,000
 He says, "You are my image on earth,"

339
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:31,000
 which means a lot of different things, but in this case, it means that you are able also to image, to be, and partner with me.

340
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:35,000
 Remember, he says to humanity, "Go into the world, bring it to flourishing,

