00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:12,000
 But then, thousands of years later, James writes to the church, and he says, "It's all hell."

372
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:14,000
 Like it's all burning.

373
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:21,000
 Like what's coming out of our mouths is setting everything on fire, and not in a good way.

