00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,000
 And he says this.

395
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,000
 Notice what he says.

396
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:31,000
 "Did God really say?"

397
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:36,000
 So the first thing that the enemy does is try to attack the structure of God speaking,

398
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:39,000
 God creating, God blessing, God bringing good.

