00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:48,000
 They're beginning to go, "Hang on a sec, now, what do we believe?"

402
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:51,000
 Because there's a new voice in the world.

403
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,000
 Are you seeing this?

