00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:06,000
 And now Adam and Eve are caught between these two narratives that are at play.

407
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:10,000
 Will they align themselves to the wonder of the Lord and the debar of Him,

408
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:16,000
 or will they now align themselves to the trickery and the destruction of the enemy?

409
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:18,000
 And here's what they do.

