00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:25,000
 and to believe and adhere to Satan,

412
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:32,000
 they change from adhering to one way of being and speaking to now aligning with another.

413
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,000
 And here's what Satan does.

414
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:40,000
 Satan speaks, Satan destroys, Satan curses, Satan pronounces death.

415
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:44,000
 So see these two things side by side right here.

416
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:48,000
 And all of this is sort of saying, all of this is driven by what comes out of the mouth.

417
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:52,000
 And here's the thing, which of these two are we going to align our lives with?

418
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:55,000
 This is why for James, this is not about some behavior modification.

419
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:59,000
 It's not like, "Hey, just try to be a nicer person in the world."

420
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:03,000
 Like this is James saying, "Don't you understand what you've been created for,

421
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:07,000
 how the world is structured, and you are either one of these things or you're the other."

422
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,000
 This is very important.

423
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:13,000
 James is essentially saying to the church, "There are no neutral words."

424
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:15,000
 Come on, church.

425
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:19,000
 Your words out of your mouth, they're either aligning yourself to what God is doing

426
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:24,000
 and brings blessing and life, or your words are aligning to the work of the enemy,

427
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:26,000
 and you're bringing death and destruction.

428
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:27,000
 There's no middle ground.

429
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:30,000
 There's no Genesis 3b.

430
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:35,000
 It's Genesis 1, 2, and 3, and then we're on a journey for redemption through Jesus Christ.

431
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:37,000
 There's a red pill and a blue pill.

432
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,000
 There's no other pill.

433
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:43,000
 That's a matrix reference for any of you who are my age.

434
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:48,000
 There's no neutral words James wants his church to know.

435
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:55,000
 You're either this or you're that, and this, he says, is the issue.

436
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:57,000
 And notice what he says at the start.

437
00:27:57,000 --> 00:28:02,000
 "We all struggle with this."

438
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:08,000
 So the question is, how do we align more to that side than that side?

439
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:15,000
 Well, when the disciple John is sitting down to write his version of the gospel,

440
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:20,000
 and he thinks, "How do I start to help people to understand who Jesus is?"

